'''Zvolen''' ([[jermanikanes]]: ''Altsohl'', [[magyarikanes]]: ''Zólyom'') si ek [[foro]] andi mashkarutni [[Slovakiya]], pashal i [[Banska Bistrica]], ko len [[Hron]]. Ando foro si ek purano mashkar vi ek [[khervaj]].

Kathe si i [[Gandhi (mashkarutni shkola ando Zvolen)|Romani Mashkarutni Shkola Gandhi]] vi kathe sas praxosarde but romane xelavde. 


